Conclusion

The Superstore achieved $2.26M in total revenue over 2015–2018 with a strong upward trajectory.

West region and Technology category are the two primary revenue engines.

Revenue grew +30.6% in 2017 and +20.8% in 2018. Q4 seasonality is consistent and predictable — it should be proactively leveraged through early campaign planning.

Phones and Chairs together contribute 29% of total revenue and deserve focused investment.

